This method looks for a recycled supplementary view of the specified type and returns it if one exists. If one does not exist, it creates it using one of the following techniques:
method to register a class for the identifier, this method instantiates your view class and returns it.
method to register a nib file for the identifier, this method loads the view from the nib file and returns it.
